## Description {#details}

This class is used to track label information.

Labels are collected from <code>DBG&#95;LABEL</code> instructions.

Definition at line 289 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/asmprinter/dwarfdebug-h">DwarfDebug.h</a>.
